{"iti60:0.1":"Itivuttaka 60 ","iti60:0.2":"Tikanipata ","iti60:0.3":"Dutiyavagga ","iti60:0.4":"Punnakiriyavatthusutta ","iti60:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti60:2.1":"“Tinimani, bhikkhave, punnakiriyavatthuni. ","iti60:2.2":"Katamani tini? ","iti60:2.3":"Danamayam punnakiriyavatthu, silamayam punnakiriyavatthu, bhavanamayam punnakiriyavatthu—","iti60:2.4":"imani kho, bhikkhave, tini punnakiriyavatthuni”ti. ","iti60:2.5":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti60:2.6":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti60:3.1":"“Punnameva so sikkheyya, ","iti60:3.2":"ayataggam sukhudrayam; ","iti60:3.3":"Dananca samacariyanca, ","iti60:3.4":"mettacittanca bhavaye. ","iti60:4.1":"Ete dhamme bhavayitva, ","iti60:4.2":"tayo sukhasamuddaye; ","iti60:4.3":"Abyabajjham sukham lokam, ","iti60:4.4":"pandito upapajjati”ti. ","iti60:5.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti60:5.2":"Pathamam. "}